Note on evidence groups:
- Each chunk carries a `tool_source` label (e.g. "dense_retrieval", "lexical_retrieval", "graph_retrieval").
- `dense_retrieval` chunks come from semantic vector search — good for conceptual questions.
- `lexical_retrieval` chunks come from exact keyword/BM25 match — good for IDs, names, and precise terms.
- `graph_retrieval` chunks come from relationship/triplet search — good for multi-hop or relational questions.
- Use the `score` field as a relevance signal when deciding which evidence to trust most.
